    "asOf": "2021-07-29",
    "date": "2021-09-01T12:38:19Z",
    "text": "Renters Tax Credit Act of 2021\n\nThis bill allows owners of rental buildings who provide reductions in rent to their low-income tenants a refundable tax credit for a specified percentage of the difference between market rent and 30% of the monthly family income of such tenants. The bill allocates credit amounts to states for distribution to participating taxpayers."
